HEADWORD: Illusive
<hw>Il*lu"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Illude</er>.]</ety> <def>Deceiving by false show; deceitful;
deceptive; false; illusory; unreal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Truth from <qex>illusive</qex> falsehood to command.</q>
<rj><qau>Thomson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Illusively</ent>⟦br⟧
